{"tid":1167220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有創意］湖南公安高層 於家中用木工鑿子插向身體多個部位「自殺」 手法惹懷疑","createTime":"2019-05-23T01:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T02:09:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"599ea2ed301219adef7116eab6c2f8b91af584b9","tid":1167220,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:56:29.000Z","msg":"日前，中共湖南張家界市公安局黨委委員、政治部主任余四清在家自殺身亡。官方稱，他是因病自殺。但消息人士對陸媒說，余四清死前將自已反鎖房間內，懷疑其用木工鑿子插向身體多個部位後死亡。網民認為不可思議。<br />\n<br />\n5月21日，湖南張家界市官方證實，余四清因不堪病痛，於20日下午在家自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n《新京報》引述前張家界市政協提案法制委主任龔厚欽的話稱，事發當日，余四清家人發現余四清將自己反鎖房間內，懷疑其用木工鑿子插向身體多個部位後死亡，致命傷在手上。現場留有遺書證實自己難忍病痛之苦很久了。<br />\n<br />\n龔厚欽還稱，3個月前，余四清曾向公安局遞交辭職書，沒被正式批准。而他患有腎病多年，還曾重金屬中毒。22日上午，余四清遺體已被送到張家界殯儀館。<br />\n<br />\n大陸網友紛紛質疑余四清之死不可思議：「這種死亡法也太殘忍了吧？」「還寫遺書證實自己不堪病痛自殺？抑鬱症=必須封口？！」「媒體和網民對官員『自殺』兩字很敏感，浮想聯翩，尤其是特殊時期。」<br />\n<br />\n公開資料顯示，現年55歲的余四清於湖南石門縣，在湖南公安系統工作30多年，先後任張家界市公安局治安支隊支隊長、張家界市永定區副區長兼永定區公安分局局長。<br />\n<br />\n2015年開始擔任張家界市公安局黨委委員、政治部主任，分管培訓中心、工會、團委、婦委會、警察基金會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ntdtv.com/b5/mkt_ipad/2019/05/22/a102583998.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2Fmkt_ipad%2F2019%2F05%2F22%2Fa102583998.html&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=4bacb8bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ntdtv.com/b5/mkt_ipad/2019/05/22/a102583998.html</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle用木工鑿子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRmXsOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRmXsOh.png&h=f0671de7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4095c1113edd433e23050c7231bbff357aad280f","tid":1167220,"uid":51672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自殺"},{"pid":"8424e1279b06de691d63dc1c89847e6515cf0ad3","tid":1167220,"uid":85557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4095c1113edd433e23050c7231bbff357aad280f","tid":1167220,"uid":51672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:07:28.000Z","msg":"被"},{"pid":"65896c54f17cbb1583b39b74a354095e4f0f34a2","tid":1167220,"uid":42340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"想扮蘇哥"},{"pid":"583276d1b07ffeb1783edfbac5d1d832cd638c07","tid":1167220,"uid":128568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/RO7Q1tMGE7g/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FRO7Q1tMGE7g%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=2518427e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}